Usage: convertBlackBoxToFence [-help] { -cell <string> | -inst <string> }

-help              # Prints out the command usage
-cell <string>     # Specifies the name of a module or submodule that should be
                   # converted to a fence. (string, optional)
-inst <string>     # Specifies the name of the blackbox instance that should be
                   # converted to a fence. (string, optional)